               <p>I live in <placeName id="t17890909-157-crimeloc762">Bishopsgate-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17890909-157-crimeloc762" type="placeName" value="Bishopsgate-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17890909-157-crimeloc762" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890909-157-off760 t17890909-157-crimeloc762"></join>; I found the prisoner in my house on the 29th of August, about two o'clock; he was secreted in a recess in the shop; I saw him there; the next witness took him from there in my presence; he said he had missed his way to his lodgings; he was examined by the watchman, who found a knife upon him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17890909-157-person1322">
                  EDWARD
                   TRUSTY
