                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am watchman; on the 29th of August, I was called in, and found the prisoner in custody; I searched him, and found this knife and two keys; they are common keys; it was about two in the morning; he was taken before a magistrate, and committed.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called four witnesses who gave him a good character.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17890909-157-verdict763" type="verdictDescription">
